            <li>Choose your preferred color style.</li>
            <li>Works on multiple monitors.</li>
            <li>Much more!</li>
          </ul>
					
				</div>

				<div class="one-third last">

					<h6>Requirements</h6>

          <p>Color Picker Pro requires Mac OS X 10.5 or higher.</p>

          <p><a href="http://fructivity.s3.amazonaws.com/ColorPickerPro/Color%20Picker%20Pro.zip" class="button active_button">Download FREE</a></p>
          <p>Or <a href="https://github.com/oscardelben/Color-Picker-Pro">fork on Github</a>.</p>
					
				</div>
					
			</div><!-- end .container -->
			
